examples:
TS k8s
| STATS distincts=count_distinct(count_distinct_over_time(network.cost)),
        distincts_imprecise=count_distinct(count_distinct_over_time(network.cost, 100))
  BY cluster, time_bucket = bucket(@timestamp,1minute)
